        <mxCell id="OdQHVJ1Rcee0M5euzhVP-78" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;fontSize=12;fontColor=#1D2D3E;fontFamily=Helvetica;" value="&lt;font face=&quot;arial&quot; color=&quot;#475e75&quot;&gt;This SAP BTP Solution Diagram depicts the SAP BTP Subaccount setup for a 3-staged environment covering a development, testing and production stage.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;arial&quot; color=&quot;#475e75&quot;&gt;Besides the pure SAP BTP Subaccount model, it shows the integration with the the stages of the SAP Cloud Identity Service tenants and the connectivity to the SAP S/4HANA Cloud Private Edition.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;arial&quot; color=&quot;#475e75&quot;&gt;The services running in separate subaccounts might also be merged depending on the overall customers SAP BTP Subaccount Model.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1070" x="20" y="844" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
